<i>in Roswaal's mansion.</i>

58
00:03:26,041 --> 00:03:29,041
<i>The first one is to earn</i>
<i>the trust of the staff here.</i>

59
00:03:29,625 --> 00:03:32,083
<i>If I don't gain the favor</i>
<i>of those two girls,</i>

60
00:03:32,166 --> 00:03:34,541
<i>they're likely to kill me</i>
<i>to keep me silent.</i>

61
00:03:36,041 --> 00:03:38,916
<i>The winning them over plan goes</i>
<i>not only for Rem and Ram</i>

62
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,375
<i>but for their master Roswaal</i>
<i>as well.</i>

63
00:03:41,458 --> 00:03:44,083
<i>And the second one</i>
<i>is to defeat the shaman</i>

64
00:03:44,166 --> 00:03:45,958
<i>that attacks his mansion.</i>

65
00:03:46,041 --> 00:03:48,125
