134
00:06:02,416 --> 00:06:04,291
- [chuckles]
And Shamac!

135
00:06:11,375 --> 00:06:13,166
- [gasps]

136
00:06:13,250 --> 00:06:15,875
[gagging]

137
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,416
[groaning]

138
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:18,666
<i>- Okay, that's it.</i>

139
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,125
- [gasping]

140
00:06:20,208 --> 00:06:21,458
- So what'd you think?

141
00:06:21,541 --> 00:06:22,791
Pretty cool, huh?

142
00:06:22,875 --> 00:06:24,250
- Are you all right?

143
00:06:26,375 --> 00:06:28,000
- Yeah, I'm totally fine!

144
00:06:28,083 --> 00:06:30,666
It's not too flashy
but it seems pretty effective.

145
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,458
So you're saying that I can use
this Shamac thing, too, right?

146
00:06:32,541 --> 00:06:35,458
- Well, that all depends
on your training.

147
00:06:35,541 --> 00:06:36,541
Do you wanna try
the beginner's course?

148
00:06:36,625 --> 00:06:39,583
- Very much so!
Please, Master!

149
00:06:40,625 --> 00:06:43,833
- I'll be here to act as support
and use the mana inside you

