163
00:07:12,708 --> 00:07:16,625
Nyom, nyom, nyom,
nyom, nyom.

164
00:07:16,708 --> 00:07:20,083
[whooshing]

165
00:07:20,166 --> 00:07:21,083
- What the--

166
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:22,250
Well, that's not good.

167
00:07:22,333 --> 00:07:23,291
Looks like the gate just--

168
00:07:23,375 --> 00:07:26,250
- [shouting]

169
00:07:30,541 --> 00:07:31,791
- Long story short,

170
00:07:31,875 --> 00:07:33,666
you don't have very good control
over your gate,

171
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:36,125
so I suggest you shouldn't
try too hard.

172
00:07:36,208 --> 00:07:38,625
- You're the one who said
I'd be fine.

173
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:40,875
- [laughs]
- That's so not cute.

174
00:07:40,958 --> 00:07:42,541
- Well, for better or for worse,

