to work anymore today.

183
00:08:01,041 --> 00:08:02,083
- No, I have to!
- [gasps]

184
00:08:02,166 --> 00:08:04,000
Don't try to overdo it!

185
00:08:04,083 --> 00:08:06,250
- This is exactly when I need
to overdo it.

186
00:08:06,333 --> 00:08:08,333
I can't waste a single day.

187
00:08:09,958 --> 00:08:11,958
- Goodness, you really
are hopeless.

188
00:08:12,041 --> 00:08:13,666
Take this.

189
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,375
- What?
[gurgles]

190
00:08:16,250 --> 00:08:18,000
- Chew it up.
- Hmm?

191
00:08:18,083 --> 00:08:20,166
- Chew it up and swallow it.
Ready?

192
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:21,375
Go.
- [grunts]

193
00:08:21,458 --> 00:08:23,666
[screams]

194
00:08:24,666 --> 00:08:25,583
Whoa.

195
00:08:25,666 --> 00:08:26,833
What did I just eat?

196
00:08:26,916 --> 00:08:28,541
- [giggles]
A little something

197
00:08:28,625 --> 00:08:30,041
called a bocco fruit.

198
00:08:30,125 --> 00:08:31,125
When you eat one of these,

199
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:32,833
