1097
00:42:53,916 --> 00:42:56,500
That is not the little puppy
from before.

1098
00:42:56,583 --> 00:42:58,916
Did it transform
into this monster?

1099
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:01,458
And was the sneaky little
bastard waiting around for me

1100
00:43:01,541 --> 00:43:03,916
