1141
00:44:49,458 --> 00:44:51,250
With this many,
I don't think it's possible.

1142
00:44:51,333 --> 00:44:52,583
- Yeah, that's what I figured.

1143
00:44:52,666 --> 00:44:54,833
In that case,
right there!

1144
00:44:54,916 --> 00:44:56,583
[blow lands]
